          <span class="ep-stat-number">4.2%<small>annual</small></span>
        </div>
        <p class="ep-glass-body">Get precise FERS annuity calculations based on your years of service, high-3 salary, and retirement date scenarios. Plan with confidence.</p>
        <a href="/services/federal-benefits/fers-calculator/" class="ep-glass-link">Calculate Your FERS Annuity →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="ep-glass-card">
        <span class="ep-glass-eyebrow">Social Security Coordination</span>
        <h3>Bridge the Gap</h3>
        <p class="ep-glass-body">Federal employees have unique Social Security considerations including the FERS supplement bridge, WEP/GPO elimination benefits, and optimal claiming strategies that coordinate with your pension.</p>
        <p class="ep-glass-body">Our specialized planning ensures you maximize both your FERS annuity and Social Security benefits through strategic timing and coordination.</p>
        <a href="/services/federal-benefits/social-security-federal/" class="ep-glass-link">Optimize Social Security →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

